{"tid":2361251,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"便宜不見得好賣？四款 iPhone 12 銷售數據顯示，iPhone 12 mini 賣得超差","createTime":"2021-01-10T13:06:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T12:04:30.000Z","uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":63,"replies":[{"pid":"d12a5b655e1e780b53323fb158c48252af1f5cd3","tid":2361251,"uid":15564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:06:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn1.techbang.com/system/excerpt_images/83627/special_headline/794c7debad8e42988ab2e007c3f13bd2.jpg?1610093244\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn1.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fexcerpt_images%2F83627%2Fspecial_headline%2F794c7debad8e42988ab2e007c3f13bd2.jpg%3F1610093244&h=694366f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蘋果在去年底推出四款 iPhone 12 機型，其中 5.4 吋的 iPhone 12 mini 是蘋果近年來少見的小尺寸 iPhone，或許是因為尺寸不符合大多數人的使用需求，根據美國消費者情報研究（CIRP）的報告，iPhone 12 mini 的銷量遠低於其他 iPhone 12 機型。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.techbang.com/system/images/583062/original/3808c3726df51ff7d309b95f568a9dab.png?1610093116\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.techbang.com%2Fsystem%2Fimages%2F583062%2Foriginal%2F3808c3726df51ff7d309b95f568a9dab.png%3F1610093116&h=c66a6be0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n統計去年（2020 年）10 月和 11 月全美銷量，iPhone 12 全系列在美國總銷量達到 76% 之高，其中，iPhone 12 是最暢銷的機型，佔了 27% 的銷售量，其次為 iPhone 12 Pro Max 以及 iPhone 12 Pro，<span class=\"red\">不過 iPhone 12 mini 的銷量只佔了 iPhone 12 系列全部銷售量的 6%。</span><br />\n<br />\nCIRP 推測 iPhone 12 mini 之所以對消費者吸引力較低，可能是因為受到更平價的 iPhone SE、iPhone XR、iPhone 11 等機型仍在販售所影響。<br />\n<br />\n相較於去年的 iPhone 11 系列，今年的 iPhone 12 系列總體看起來更為暢銷，去年同期 iPhone 11 總銷量為 69%，其中 iPhone 11 是最熱賣的機型，佔了全部 iPhone 11 系列銷量的 39%，而 iPhone 11 Pro 以及 iPhone 11 Pro Max 則佔了剩餘的 30%。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.techbang.com/posts/83627-four-iphone-12?fbclid=IwAR2sb792TZXPKrWlnXQp1MPOZQf1vcZvbLfcGW6hN5aeg-74UPaEEo2omEU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.techbang.com%2Fposts%2F83627-four-iphone-12%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2sb792TZXPKrWlnXQp1MPOZQf1vcZvbLfcGW6hN5aeg-74UPaEEo2omEU&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7QNVisxpnNpADW7ISUiLTyw%3D&h=fe3676fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.techbang.com/posts/83627-four-iphone-12?fbclid=IwAR2sb792TZXPKrWlnXQp1MPOZQf1vcZvbLfcGW6hN5aeg-74UPaEEo2omEU</a>"},{"pid":"eda8194bc8b48f9538757eb8fb162864e76e2698","tid":2361251,"uid":9,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:18:51.000Z","msg":"減價我換"},{"pid":"be555fdce176f3404e47c7cd86084bb8ccee05b3","tid":2361251,"uid":24282,"like":46,"dislike":2,"score":44,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:19:51.000Z","msg":"係連登仔先吹奏細機"},{"pid":"76086d3b4c2d469eaa0d418836214f5a70911596","tid":2361251,"uid":55458,"like":87,"dislike":1,"score":86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:20:16.000Z","msg":"班連登狗仲話會大賣<br />\n俾佢地做CEO真係蘋果都破產"},{"pid":"5d4cd17914577eaa01500ce4d25b014349d7d8b3","tid":2361251,"uid":29167,"like":4,"dislike":14,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:20:18.000Z","msg":"講真我訂咗12pro 依家好想換12mini <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ad7c63a6a407f18d2c34a68a1f559beadd0f1bf","tid":2361251,"uid":71748,"like":9,"dislike":18,"score":-9,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:21:15.000Z","msg":"得單卡加esim先係死因"},{"pid":"1a4924dff6b1ae94a970a6a4faff599d77f20e15","tid":2361251,"uid":10290,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:21:39.000Z","msg":"個個都要大mon大電仲吹奏夠輕單手操作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ed5e14b05d2041dc4f8cbd12a9554382cbb7376","tid":2361251,"uid":250308,"like":39,"dislike":0,"score":39,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T13:22:52.000Z","msg":"笑死，插xr 720p就大賣，捧mini就銷情慘淡，燈仔d眼光<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07b1bb41d33acd88ab329f4067ff045187cacf22","tid":2361251,"uid":315881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"repl